Job1 : GIT/GITHUB + Jenkins --> uploaded the code

Job2 : MAVEN + JENKINS --> build the code (compile + unit test (junit) + Package) --> .jar / .war / .ear --> artifacts
Job3:  Deployment the code to QA env --> (DOCKER, KUBERNETES, ANSIBLE) + Jenkins
Job4: Functional/Automation Testing (SIT) --> (Selenium, testng) + Jenkins
Job5: Performance Testing --> JMeter + Jenkins
Job6: Security Testing --> (Fortify, SonarQube) + Jenkins
Job7: UAT Testing --> User Acceptance Testing 

Job8 : Deploy the code to Production --> (DOCKER, KUBERNETES, ANSIBLE) + Jenkins

Monitoring (24*7) , Feedback

Objective --> 

DevOps Lifecycles:
1. Continuous Development
2. Continuous Testing
3. Continuous Integration
4. Continuous Deployment
5. Continuous Monitoring/Feedback
